---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="Privacy Policy — ostk" description="Privacy policy for ostk software and the ostk.ai website.">
  <div class="container">
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="meta"><em>Effective: 2026-03-11</em> &middot; <a href="mailto:contact@ostk.ai">contact@ostk.ai</a></p>

    <h2>Summary</h2>
    <p>The software collects nothing. It runs locally on your machine — no telemetry, no phone-home. The website uses Plausible Analytics for aggregate page view counts only: no cookies, no personal data.</p>

    <h2>The software</h2>
    <p>ostk runs entirely on your local machine. It does not:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Send data to any server</li>
      <li>Collect usage statistics</li>
      <li>Phone home for license checks</li>
      <li>Upload files, logs, or audit trails</li>
      <li>Require network access for any core functionality</li>
    </ul>
    <p>All state lives in your filesystem under <code>.haystack/</code> in your repository. You own it. You can read it. You can delete it.</p>

    <h2>The website (ostk.ai)</h2>
    <p>ostk uses Plausible Analytics — a privacy-first analytics tool with no cookies,
no cross-site tracking, and full GDPR/CCPA compliance. Only aggregate page view
counts and outbound link clicks are recorded. No personal data is collected.</p>
    <p>The ostk.ai website:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Does not use cookies</li>
      <li>Does not track individual visitors</li>
      <li>Does not collect personal information</li>
      <li>Uses Plausible Analytics for aggregate page view counts and outbound link clicks only</li>
      <li>Serves static content only</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>needle-bench leaderboard</h2>
    <p>If you submit benchmark scores to the public leaderboard, the following is published:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Model name</li>
      <li>Provider name</li>
      <li>Scenario scores</li>
      <li>Submission timestamp</li>
    </ul>
    <p>No personal information is required or stored with submissions.</p>

    <h2>Third parties</h2>
    <p>The website uses <a href="https://plausible.io">Plausible Analytics</a> (plausible.io), which processes only aggregate, anonymous page view data. No personal data is shared. The software shares no data with any third party.</p>

    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>Questions about this policy: <a href="mailto:contact@ostk.ai">contact@ostk.ai</a></p>
  </div>
</Base>

<style>
  .meta {
    color: var(--ostk-text-muted);
    font-size: var(--ostk-text-sm);
    margin-bottom: var(--ostk-space-8);
  }
  .meta a {
    color: var(--ostk-text-muted);
  }
  .meta a:hover {
    color: var(--ostk-text-secondary);
  }
</style>
